WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:15.000
Downloaded From AnimeArcadia.lk

00:00:20.563 --> 00:00:23.855
Our job isn't over just because you blew up the plane!

00:00:25.980 --> 00:00:29.771
It ain't over until you get to my brother, you hybrid.

00:00:29.855 --> 00:00:33.605
Please, don't let me fall to my death.

00:00:34.813 --> 00:00:38.938
Then I will kill you with my own hands! Do you understand?

00:00:41.605 --> 00:00:42.813
Try not to die?

00:00:43.563 --> 00:00:44.771
That's it!

00:01:05.480 --> 00:01:08.271
"Based on a video game series produced by Capcom"

00:01:59.688 --> 00:02:02.771
"Devil May Cry"

00:02:03.730 --> 00:02:06.646
"Produced by Adi Shankar"

00:02:35.271 --> 00:02:38.396
Have you found any pests in this building?

00:02:39.146 --> 00:02:41.480
Go, go on another mission.

00:02:42.563 --> 00:02:45.313
That Sapiens bitch, Plasma and I will take care of it.

00:02:45.813 --> 00:02:48.313
Of course you can do it alone

00:02:48.396 --> 00:02:49.938
'For Makai'

00:02:52.521 --> 00:02:54.313
'For Makai'

00:03:05.896 --> 00:03:06.938
What's going on?

00:03:07.021 --> 00:03:09.313
"Police cordon, no entry"

00:03:09.396 --> 00:03:13.646
Damn, I don't know what's going on in there, but just don't pay me overtime.

00:03:13.730 --> 00:03:15.688
Are you from the attack scene?

00:03:15.771 --> 00:03:19.313
Yes, the PR team will have a hard time clearing up that mess.

00:03:19.396 --> 00:03:21.688
The usable equipment was retrieved from the truck.

00:03:21.771 --> 00:03:23.688
Let's settle down and wait

00:03:23.771 --> 00:03:26.646
Because the high voltage makes it impossible to enter the interior

00:03:26.730 --> 00:03:29.771
But as soon as the door opens, it will move.

00:03:50.271 --> 00:03:51.896
The Cavalier is here, wake up!

00:03:54.063 --> 00:03:56.730
Is it finally time to give the intruders a taste?

00:03:56.813 --> 00:03:59.563
Now go into battle

00:04:50.146 --> 00:04:52.730
It's because of the drugs, I'm hallucinating

00:05:06.271 --> 00:05:07.396
Fuck

00:05:17.521 --> 00:05:19.271
shoot a gun

00:05:21.021 --> 00:05:23.938
please

00:05:33.980 --> 00:05:34.980
Lieutenant

00:05:35.855 --> 00:05:39.646
I almost got you right, but I'm glad I saw your face.

00:05:40.230 --> 00:05:41.271
Same thing

00:05:45.396 --> 00:05:46.980
Dante!

00:05:47.063 --> 00:05:48.563
Do something!

00:05:48.646 --> 00:05:50.396
Do you have any good suggestions?

00:05:50.480 --> 00:05:55.480
I don't know, maybe try turning your arms into pointy ones again

00:05:56.355 --> 00:06:00.313
Superheroes can fly around in suits, so why can't you?

00:06:00.396 --> 00:06:02.438
There has to be a parachute coming out of the belt!

00:06:02.521 --> 00:06:03.521
Yeah, parachute!

00:06:20.646 --> 00:06:21.688
Got it!

00:06:23.271 --> 00:06:25.021
This is my first time using a parachute.

00:06:25.105 --> 00:06:27.855
Well, it was my first time on an airplane.

00:06:28.355 --> 00:06:31.563
Don't worry, this time it'll go much better than before.

00:06:33.230 --> 00:06:34.396
Dante, wake up

00:06:36.063 --> 00:06:37.521
You won't die

00:07:04.855 --> 00:07:06.730
I feel weird!

00:07:06.813 --> 00:07:07.855
I'm weird too!

00:07:07.938 --> 00:07:11.396
We're falling from the sky at 160 kilometers per hour right now!

00:07:12.271 --> 00:07:13.813
It feels weird!

00:07:15.563 --> 00:07:18.188
- How did you survive? - I guess I was lucky.

00:07:19.021 --> 00:07:20.021
Give me the gun

00:07:51.063 --> 00:07:53.480
Aren't they all already dead?

00:07:54.605 --> 00:07:58.605
Yeah, if you just shatter it into pieces it'll be harder to figure out.

00:07:58.688 --> 00:08:00.355
One floor above is the top floor

00:08:00.438 --> 00:08:02.105
The amulet is still there

00:08:02.188 --> 00:08:06.021
Let's go see what third-rate Roger Rabbit is up to there.

00:08:06.105 --> 00:08:08.313
The stairs to the upper floor are at the end of the hallway.

00:08:08.396 --> 00:08:12.896
I had time to scout while I was hiding here.

00:08:15.563 --> 00:08:18.063
Have you been inside the apartment?

00:08:18.146 --> 00:08:19.771
No, what about you, Lieutenant?

00:08:19.855 --> 00:08:20.688
Only one house

00:08:20.771 --> 00:08:23.688
The ones that rabbit guy has locked up aren't people, they're demons.

00:08:23.771 --> 00:08:26.563
But those demons were different

00:08:26.646 --> 00:08:29.271
They cared for each other like family

00:08:29.355 --> 00:08:32.105
But still, the devil is the devil, right?

00:08:32.188 --> 00:08:34.480
I'm not like the guys I was trained to kill.

00:08:34.563 --> 00:08:37.438
I feel like there's something much more complicated going on

00:08:38.105 --> 00:08:41.063
I remember something I witnessed with my team before.

00:08:41.146 --> 00:08:42.646
It doesn't matter anymore

00:08:42.730 --> 00:08:44.730
It doesn't seem complicated at all.

00:08:44.813 --> 00:08:47.521
They are devils we are devil hunters

00:08:47.605 --> 00:08:51.105
I guarantee you that there is nothing good about people from Makai.

00:08:52.355 --> 00:08:54.230
Are you talking about the 'demon world'?

00:09:03.855 --> 00:09:05.938
I've benefited from your kindness.

00:09:06.021 --> 00:09:09.730
Now there is no need to fight as a human.

00:09:23.855 --> 00:09:25.271
You were there

00:09:41.813 --> 00:09:42.813
for a moment!

00:09:45.021 --> 00:09:46.521
How about negotiating?

00:09:47.230 --> 00:09:52.438
I don't think you're in a position to offer anything great right now.

00:09:52.521 --> 00:09:56.896
If your goal was to kill me, you wouldn't have had to transform.

00:09:56.980 --> 00:09:59.480
Did the rabbit give you another mission?

00:10:00.105 --> 00:10:02.730
Mission to infiltrate Darkcom

00:10:08.521 --> 00:10:10.396
What do you want to say?

00:10:10.896 --> 00:10:13.980
You used the body of a low-ranking soldier.

00:10:14.063 --> 00:10:17.271
I'm an officer, I can go into places that are forbidden to lower-ranking soldiers.

00:10:18.230 --> 00:10:21.771
I can hand over all the information and passwords.

00:10:21.855 --> 00:10:24.230
As long as I live

00:10:41.855 --> 00:10:42.896
for a moment!

00:10:46.313 --> 00:10:48.938
Rabbit wanted to hurt you the most

00:10:49.021 --> 00:10:53.521
It is my honor to offer you my corpse swollen with poison.

00:10:58.313 --> 00:11:00.396
I think he killed another woman

00:11:20.730 --> 00:11:23.063
Dante! What's wrong?

00:11:25.188 --> 00:11:27.563
Son of Spada

00:11:28.521 --> 00:11:31.521
Your father left you something. You must always protect it.

00:11:33.521 --> 00:11:36.438
They're here! Where did you go, bro?

00:11:38.105 --> 00:11:40.063
Hide, Mom has to find Virgil.

00:12:10.813 --> 00:12:13.146
Hey! You had wings?

00:12:14.230 --> 00:12:17.521
Then hurry up and flap your wings and save us!

00:12:21.188 --> 00:12:24.688
No! Get out of here! You're in league with those guys! Get out!

00:12:25.271 --> 00:12:26.146
Then just fall!

00:12:28.688 --> 00:12:32.521
Do you understand now? Even the devil can do the work of God.

00:12:35.438 --> 00:12:36.855
Hey, you guy!

00:12:42.146 --> 00:12:43.980
Dante!

00:13:00.146 --> 00:13:03.063
Son of Sparda, I'll kill you!

00:13:58.896 --> 00:14:00.688
It's time to change things

00:14:00.771 --> 00:14:02.146
"Unlock the entrance"

00:14:03.563 --> 00:14:05.563
"Warning Unauthorized Access"

00:14:10.063 --> 00:14:12.146
Now is the time to move!

00:14:20.188 --> 00:14:24.146
Stay back! Do not approach the building. It's a trap!

00:14:26.688 --> 00:14:28.396
I repeat! This is a trap!

00:14:31.646 --> 00:14:34.188
- Everyone, fall back! - Repeat!

00:14:38.730 --> 00:14:41.605
I'm glad to see you've awakened your inner demon.

00:14:41.688 --> 00:14:44.813
I thought it would be pathetic to kill a human just to get revenge

00:14:44.896 --> 00:14:47.896
Do you know how I felt when I killed your brother?

00:14:48.480 --> 00:14:49.396
I didn't feel anything

00:15:35.396 --> 00:15:37.188
You took my stuff

00:15:37.271 --> 00:15:40.021
I'd kill you all if I could just get it back.

00:15:40.605 --> 00:15:42.230
I'll kill the rest too

00:15:47.105 --> 00:15:50.521
Where is my necklace?

00:15:57.105 --> 00:15:58.813
Rabbit has it

00:15:58.896 --> 00:16:00.396
I don't know either

00:16:10.646 --> 00:16:13.063
I think I just revealed my location

00:16:17.063 --> 00:16:18.271
Report the situation

00:16:19.105 --> 00:16:22.230
There are two casualties, but the rest are alive.

00:16:23.396 --> 00:16:26.896
Thank goodness we already lost one team today.

00:16:26.980 --> 00:16:28.646
I thought you all lost too

00:16:29.146 --> 00:16:31.313
It's so nice to hear your voice, Lieutenant.

00:16:31.396 --> 00:16:33.313
There's something else I need to tell you

00:16:33.396 --> 00:16:35.480
Gather everyone

00:16:35.563 --> 00:16:36.688
"On air"

00:16:37.688 --> 00:16:42.355
If the devil… no, the Macaians can hear me now

00:16:42.438 --> 00:16:46.563
I am Lieutenant Mary Ann Arkham of Darkcom.

00:16:47.355 --> 00:16:50.563
I know you didn't come here to attack us.

00:16:51.855 --> 00:16:54.271
The reason you had to come to the human world was

00:16:54.355 --> 00:16:56.938
Because we were in an environment where survival was impossible

00:16:57.438 --> 00:17:02.813
I also know that the White Rabbit has you locked up and is making you tremble in fear.

00:17:03.813 --> 00:17:05.563
That ends today

00:17:06.271 --> 00:17:10.646
My team will enter here and guide you to safety.

00:17:11.563 --> 00:17:14.355
This is purely a rescue mission.

00:17:16.105 --> 00:17:17.813
You guys have been

00:17:19.063 --> 00:17:23.271
I also know that you have been hurt by people like us.

00:17:24.730 --> 00:17:26.938
You are not our enemies

00:17:27.438 --> 00:17:29.063
Our enemy is the rabbit

00:17:29.146 --> 00:17:34.188
I intend to repay all the suffering he caused.

00:17:37.063 --> 00:17:38.188
Do you understand?

00:17:38.896 --> 00:17:41.105
I understood what you said, but…

00:17:41.188 --> 00:17:42.605
The reason why it has to be like that is…

00:17:42.688 --> 00:17:45.688
Let me tell you why. The demons here are not warriors.

00:17:45.771 --> 00:17:47.105
They are just refugees

00:17:47.188 --> 00:17:50.271
I came to this world thanks to the device that the rabbit had.

00:17:50.355 --> 00:17:52.646
They had no choice but to follow the rabbit

00:17:53.146 --> 00:17:56.438
It was thanks to their help that I was able to survive.

00:17:56.521 --> 00:17:57.771
I owe you a favor

00:17:58.355 --> 00:18:00.396
So what do we do with the refugees?

00:18:00.480 --> 00:18:04.146
Let's put him in the truck and take him to headquarters and meet him there.

00:18:04.230 --> 00:18:05.813
What are you going to do, Lieutenant?

00:18:08.188 --> 00:18:10.688
I'm gonna shove that bunny up my asshole

00:18:10.771 --> 00:18:12.730
You can't get out without the help of a magician.

00:18:30.646 --> 00:18:33.230
You are just a hybrid

00:19:11.146 --> 00:19:13.063
Rabbit is not here now

00:19:15.730 --> 00:19:18.146
Should I leave a message?

00:19:18.230 --> 00:19:19.105
okay

00:19:30.813 --> 00:19:31.938
I know that person

00:19:32.521 --> 00:19:35.146
- Lady - What the hell happened?

00:19:37.313 --> 00:19:38.813
You were right

00:19:39.896 --> 00:19:41.271
Half of me is a devil

00:19:41.771 --> 00:19:43.063
Who said no?

00:19:43.146 --> 00:19:45.938
When did you get enlightenment with that rusty head?

00:19:46.021 --> 00:19:48.230
I turned into a demon 5 minutes ago

00:19:48.313 --> 00:19:50.063
It's not nonsense

00:19:50.146 --> 00:19:53.146
Even you wouldn't be able to come up with such nonsense.

00:19:53.230 --> 00:19:55.688
It's not going to change again now, is it?

00:19:55.771 --> 00:19:57.896
No, I don't feel that way.

00:19:59.480 --> 00:20:02.605
You came here because of my necklace too?

00:20:02.688 --> 00:20:04.230
How did you know where the necklace was?

00:20:04.313 --> 00:20:05.813
I followed the explosion

00:20:05.896 --> 00:20:08.480
It's worth following those rules in life.

00:20:09.480 --> 00:20:11.480
I guess you're not going to shoot me?

00:20:12.105 --> 00:20:15.521
Burn me alive? Inject explosives into my body?

00:20:15.605 --> 00:20:18.313
What about the trick of having someone pick up a grenade and then detonate it?

00:20:18.396 --> 00:20:21.688
Let's start by looking for the amulet and thinking about it.

00:20:23.605 --> 00:20:25.521
The location of the amulet is…

00:20:27.521 --> 00:20:28.438
Here it is

00:20:47.230 --> 00:20:48.605
Disgusting bastard

00:20:54.938 --> 00:20:58.146
Just to confirm, is my necklace here? Or is it…

00:21:11.105 --> 00:21:12.313
Dante

00:21:14.063 --> 00:21:16.230
And Lieutenant Arkham

00:21:16.813 --> 00:21:19.605
When I looked, Rudra was already…

00:21:19.688 --> 00:21:22.146
It's seeping into your floor.

00:21:23.271 --> 00:21:25.646
He will be remembered as a martyr.

00:21:26.146 --> 00:21:27.980
Anyway, I wanted to talk to you guys

00:21:35.230 --> 00:21:36.980
Are you going to take us to safety?

00:21:55.563 --> 00:21:58.480
Sergeant, William Baines, do you copy?

00:21:59.063 --> 00:22:00.605
Vice President?

00:22:00.688 --> 00:22:03.646
What's the situation over there? Is the amulet okay?

00:22:05.021 --> 00:22:06.355
Take it easy!

00:22:07.521 --> 00:22:09.938
It was better when I was caught by other guys

00:22:10.021 --> 00:22:10.896
what?

00:22:10.980 --> 00:22:14.938
Why are you bringing the demons alive to headquarters?

00:22:15.021 --> 00:22:16.938
Because they are refugees

00:22:17.021 --> 00:22:21.855
Don't you think it's contradictory to say a refugee from hell?

00:22:26.146 --> 00:22:29.188
Know that the trap you set was counterproductive.

00:22:29.271 --> 00:22:32.521
Because I destroyed your Nazi Frankenstein lab.

00:22:32.605 --> 00:22:36.938
The family you locked up here is also being evacuated now.

00:22:37.021 --> 00:22:38.063
It's all over

00:22:38.563 --> 00:22:41.188
Insignificant things are merely a means to an end.

00:22:41.271 --> 00:22:43.605
But your thoughts are valid, Lieutenant.

00:22:43.688 --> 00:22:45.813
It's all over

00:22:45.896 --> 00:22:48.146
My army will soon land in this city.

00:22:48.230 --> 00:22:50.355
It will cause unimaginable death

00:22:50.438 --> 00:22:54.105
I don't know if Dante would come to see us first.

00:22:54.188 --> 00:22:56.480
- 30 to you… - Don't talk nonsense.

00:22:57.146 --> 00:22:58.938
Which part doesn't make sense?

00:22:59.021 --> 00:23:02.980
It's obvious, you're going to use me as bait to lure me into another complicated trap.

00:23:03.063 --> 00:23:06.313
- That's his specialty. - What's the reason? What's different?

00:23:06.813 --> 00:23:09.688
He has all the amulets, and even Sparda's sword.

00:23:09.771 --> 00:23:12.230
I have everything I need to break down the wall.

00:23:12.313 --> 00:23:14.813
But why haven't you torn it down until now?

00:23:15.813 --> 00:23:18.271
Tell me yourself, Lieutenant.

00:23:18.771 --> 00:23:21.230
He had the chance to kill you, but he didn't.

00:23:21.730 --> 00:23:23.355
Why did you keep it alive?

00:23:23.438 --> 00:23:25.021
What the hell are you?

00:23:25.771 --> 00:23:28.063
I'm Sparda's son, so does that explain it?

00:23:28.646 --> 00:23:29.605
what?

00:23:31.105 --> 00:23:33.230
Dante has Sparda's DNA

00:23:33.313 --> 00:23:36.813
Sparda must have used his own blood to build the wall.

00:23:36.896 --> 00:23:38.646
Damn, and there's still more

00:23:38.730 --> 00:23:40.396
That's what you need

00:23:41.105 --> 00:23:42.688
Dante's Blood

00:23:42.771 --> 00:23:46.771
But before he turned into a demon, something in his DNA was dormant.

00:23:46.855 --> 00:23:49.480
So it was useless before

00:23:49.980 --> 00:23:52.438
Eat some shit, I figured it all out.

00:23:52.521 --> 00:23:55.230
I figured out your intentions.

00:23:55.313 --> 00:23:56.396
that's right

00:23:56.480 --> 00:24:00.480
We both know that that arrogant Dante is coming.

00:24:19.813 --> 00:24:20.646
oh my god

00:24:24.480 --> 00:24:26.563
It took quite a while to get in

00:24:27.063 --> 00:24:30.063
It's safe here, just corpses strewn about.

00:24:39.646 --> 00:24:41.980
Your poison was pretty nasty

00:24:42.563 --> 00:24:46.646
But looking at you, it wasn't as bad as that bullet.

00:24:49.521 --> 00:24:52.063
I'll give you 30 minutes, son of Spada.

00:24:52.146 --> 00:24:54.271
If you don't come within that time

00:24:54.355 --> 00:24:58.771
If there is even the slightest hint of Darkcom or military approach,

00:24:59.271 --> 00:25:02.271
I will give the order to attack.

00:25:11.896 --> 00:25:14.188
Notify Darkcom agents

00:25:14.688 --> 00:25:16.230
I am Vice President Baines.

00:25:17.271 --> 00:25:20.188
I nullify and change the orders you have received.

00:25:24.355 --> 00:25:25.938
What happens now, Mom?

00:25:33.271 --> 00:25:35.938
Eliminate the demon invaders

00:25:36.021 --> 00:25:37.396
Without leaving a single one behind

00:25:56.188 --> 00:25:59.521
The judgment of this world has already begun

00:26:00.021 --> 00:26:04.813
All you can do is make it less painful

00:26:07.105 --> 00:26:08.771
It's a showdown between me and the demon army.

00:26:09.271 --> 00:26:10.771
I don't think it will be difficult

00:26:11.563 --> 00:26:12.688
What did you find?

00:26:14.021 --> 00:26:16.146
I wasn't just after your amulet.

00:26:16.980 --> 00:26:20.521
His purpose was to destroy Darkcom.

00:26:20.605 --> 00:26:21.771
"A Vice President Who Doesn't Hide in the Shadows"

00:26:26.271 --> 00:26:28.605
They killed them all, everyone

00:26:30.646 --> 00:26:34.938
I can't take the world away from you killer apes,

00:26:35.771 --> 00:26:39.688
I can give you a taste of hell

00:26:46.855 --> 00:26:48.938
For Makai!

00:26:49.021 --> 00:26:49.980
"warning"

00:26:58.646 --> 00:26:59.771
"warning"

00:28:20.730 --> 00:28:22.438
"In Memory of Kevin Conroy (1955-2022)"

29:00.521 --> 29:03.313
♪ The devil's cry ♪